{"tid":518384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明點解有D人講野可以咁有自信+唔要面","createTime":"2018-01-03T09:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T11:34:28.000Z","uid":79353,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d213466402950c515f37656de0841590ce037b1c","tid":518384,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:03:02.000Z","msg":"首先，講明先，我自己都讀唔到書，但我唔會唔要面到覺得自己有資格安慰人，從而發表以下言論：<br />\n<br />\n&quot;人要有適當放鬆，讀書唔係人生全部，讀書叻唔一定第日搵到食，D人對自己太高要求、去迎合社會價值觀只會令自己辛苦勞碌一世...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n之類意思的言論<br />\n但係呢位人兄DSE只得個位數字分數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n情況就好似一個朝不保夕既中三畢業生 (其實係成績太差俾學校踢左出黎)<br />\n玩殘左搞到半夜入急症睇醫生，之後串班醫生護士&quot;睇下你地幾可憐，半夜都要開工...&quot; 乜柒物柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總結：　哪兒來的自信　<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9658c364048d946aeeab546d8a2ae547e468ba2","tid":518384,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:21:13.000Z","msg":"做咩負評<br />\n<br />\n我有講錯咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21f743d6d83b2a6bc0b94145c319e59ea1bf198","tid":518384,"uid":19062,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"咁佢講得無錯wo"},{"pid":"9622b294fe5b6baa0feaa6a7d06cfe33593c1423","tid":518384,"uid":22227,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9834aa09c25071ba6dc972791fb2048a11f29864","tid":518384,"uid":103257,"like":1,"dislike"